column2: TINDAKMALAYSIA NETWORK SERVICES PLT (TINDAK MALAYSIA)

Election Commission of Malaysia (SPR), Tindak Malaysia (2023), Attorney General Chambers, Berita Harian (https://www.bharian.com.my/berita/nasional/2023/09/1155225/prk-dun-pelangai-amizar-abu-adam-diumum-calon-bn), Utusan Malaysia (https://www.utusan.com.my/berita/2023/09/pn-calon-semula-cikgu-kasim-di-pelangai/), Blogger.com (https://www.blogger.com/profile/09199270555057034252)

This is the non-gazetted official results from SPR. The values of Voting Channel 2 (Saluran 2) of Simpang Pelangai is an estimated value as the result wasn't displayed properly from SPR Fb live. All early voters became postal voters.  TindakMalaysia Network Services PLT is not responsible for any errors or ommissions arising from the original data or its derivatives
